            "text": "to desegment the output ; \r",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "parent": 7,
            "text": "previous studies have desegmented the 1-best output from the decoder . <S>\r",
            "relation": "BACKGROUND"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "parent": 0,
            "text": "In this paper , we expand our translation options \r",
            "relation": "ROOT"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "parent": 7,
            "text": "by desegmenting n-best lists or lattices . <S>\r",
            "relation": "MANNER-MEANS"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "parent": 7,
            "text": "Our novel lattice desegmentation algorithm effectively combines both segmented and desegmented views of the target language for a large subspace of possible translation outputs , \r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "which allows for inclusion of features \r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
