            "text": "related to the desegmentation process , \r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "parent": 10,
            "text": "as well as an unsegmented language model ( LM ) . <S>\r",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 13,
            "parent": 14,
            "text": "We investigate this technique in the context of English-to-Arabic and English-to-Finnish translation , \r",
            "relation": "MANNER-MEANS"
        },
